{"tid":2361310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"WhatsApp資料焗傳fb 用戶轉投Signal","createTime":"2021-01-10T14:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T14:40:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f658f6cd9fcef9c05ae07d872c7c6fd6564ecd68","tid":2361310,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/2SDQKGJNYZACLLKEW6BHV7K4WE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2F2SDQKGJNYZACLLKEW6BHV7K4WE%2F&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7aC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=4f5ebc5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2F2SDQKGJNYZACLLKEW6BHV7K4WE%2F&h=0688a978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/2SDQKGJNYZACLLKEW6BHV7K4WE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp資料焗傳fb 用戶轉投Signal<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sCibia7-Bxh2jSGTtUXkRYUWO1Y=/661x639/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZMV6L33L3FFKVMT5NX5ABL6EPE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsCibia7-Bxh2jSGTtUXkRYUWO1Y%3D%2F661x639%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZMV6L33L3FFKVMT5NX5ABL6EPE.gif&h=ab53ae9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■WhatsApp上周向用戶發送通知，強迫他們同意將更多個人資料分享給母公司fb。<br />\n<br />\n港人最常用的手機通訊程式WhatsApp近日出現私隱爭議，表明下月起用戶資料會傳到母公司facebook；此舉得罪不少用戶，紛紛轉用加密通信程式Signal，號召者包括剛成世界首富的美國創科富豪馬斯克（Elon Musk）。<br />\n<br />\n擁有逾20億用戶的WhatsApp，上周四向大部份用戶寄更新用戶條款通知，強迫他們同意下月起將更多個人資料分享給母公司fb，包括聯絡人名單和電話號碼等，估計是為推動網上商機。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克加持 Signal用戶急增<br />\n<br />\n消息傳出後，下載加密通信程式Signal新用戶顯著增加，致令以手機傳送驗證碼都出現延誤；由數據私隱倡議者開發的Signal，以保護私隱為賣點，不會與第三方分享用戶資料，活躍用戶約1,000萬至2,000萬。<br />\n<br />\n推動熱潮的其中一名「代言名人」是馬斯克，前日他先推文以骨牌迷因嘲笑fb，是個以品評大學女性起家的網站，將不尊重別人的歪風傳開去，終至上周三暴徒踐踏國會；同日稍後直接推文兩個字「用Signal」，號召WhatsApp用家轉會，推文獲20萬人按讚。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克2018年已表明不喜fb，「無關政治，這平台令我心驚膽顫」，他同年響應號召，刪走了名下公司Tesla和SpaceX在該平台的專頁。<br />\n<br />\n關注網民保障的法國組織「La Quadrature du net」律師邁薩德（Arthur Messaud）。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日電訊報》／德國之聲"},{"pid":"6bd570f8664b94e8586fbaa5b7db4c004eb82912","tid":2361310,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:11:58.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"bdd9e2cc4db950f7fecf4392766dcef81e8df5b0","tid":2361310,"uid":56138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:38:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">終至上周三暴徒踐踏國會</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7fe68c75a563c2419f981ee67a232ab47766e2","tid":2361310,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdd9e2cc4db950f7fecf4392766dcef81e8df5b0","tid":2361310,"uid":56138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:38:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">終至上周三暴徒踐踏國會</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:40:48.000Z","msg":"蘋果不嬲買民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}